name: Paul Dennis
description: I am a very cheerful person, I always believe in the best and that is why I am very happy about my life. I am very kind and reliable and my parents say I am very independent. And my ex will never say bad things about me. I love doing a lot of things, the most I just like to pause and really enjoy the moment of my life. I like to be active, so I love outdoors but also indoors. Even though I like quiet times too. and I will be happy to learn more things in this life and share them with my beloved woman!
